snippet.title: Gully | Official Trailer | 2021 | A Crime Drama Movie
snippet.description:
Crime | Drama 

Release Date : 4 June 2021 

Cast : Jacob Latimore, Charlie Plummer, Jonathan Majors, Kelvin Harrison Jr., Amber Heard and Terrence Howard

Director : Nabil Elderkin

Plot : Three friends from a rough Los Angeles neighborhood embark on a wild night of out-of-control partying. But when the rampage stops, the retribution begins..
